@startuml state_charger
!theme plain
title Charger State Machine\n(Sommerville Ch.5 - Event-driven Model)

[*] --> Available : Charger sisteme eklenir

Available --> Occupied : Rezervasyon olusturuldu\nve sarj basladi
Available --> Offline : Operator bakim icin\noffline yapar\n/ tum rez. iptal + iade (UC3)

Occupied --> Available : Sarj oturumu\ntamamlandi\n/ charger serbest
Occupied --> Offline : Operator acil\noffline yapar\n/ aktif oturum sonlandirilir + iade

Offline --> Available : Bakim tamamlandi\nOperator aktif eder\n/ charger tekrar rez.'a acik

state Available #90EE90
state Occupied #FFD700
state Offline #FF6B6B

note right of Available
  Renk Kodu (Ch.7):
  Yesil = Available
  Sari = Occupied
  Kirmizi = Offline
end note

@enduml
